data.description: **Kitchen and living/dining rooms recently updated with neutral paint!** This charming home sits on a 1.13 acre lot. Step inside and you'll immediately notice the abundance of natural light that floods the great room! The sunlit space creates a warm and welcoming ambiance that is ideal for entertaining! The primary bedroom is a private sanctuary, located on the opposite side of the home from the other bedrooms. It features an en-suite and walk-in closet. The main living area is rounded out by a large sliding glass door overlooking the ample backyard, 2 bedrooms and a full guest bathroom. Adjacent to the large open kitchen is a pantry, mudroom, and large bonus room! Recently updated with a new roof, exterior paint, and gutters, this home offers peace of mind and ensures years of worry-free living. Additionally, the property's location provides easy access to local amenities, Kings Bay, schools, and major roadways, making daily commutes a breeze. Don't miss the chance to make this Kingsland gem your own! Schedule your private tour today and envision the possibilities that await you.
